        "type": "text",
        "text": "由 $a f(h) + b f(2h) - f(0) = o(h)$ ，得 $\\lim_{h\\to 0}\\frac{af(h) + bf(2h) - f(0)}{h} = \\lim_{h\\to 0}\\frac{o(h)}{h} = 0$ ",
